General.Name: Vital Farms Inc
General.Description: Vital Farms, Inc., a food company, packages, markets, and distributes shell eggs, butter, and other products in the United States. It produces products sourced from animals raised on family farms, including shell eggs, butter, hard-boiled eggs, and liquid whole eggs under the Vital Farms brand and other trade names. The company provides its products through third parties and direct to retailers, and commercial and non-commercial foodservice operators. Vital Farms, Inc. was founded in 2007 and is headquartered in Austin, Texas.
